    "title": "Braised Eggs with Leek and Za\u2019atar",
    "description": "This is a quick way to get a very comforting meal on the table in a wonderfully short amount of time. It\u2019s a dish as happily eaten for brunch, with coffee, as it is for a light supper with some crusty white bread and a glass of wine. The leeks and spinach can be made up to a day ahead and kept in the fridge, ready for the eggs to be cracked in and braised.",
